description.simpleText:
On this episode of Chuckle Sandwich, we brought Joe Bartolozzi back onto the podcast to help us utilize his superior moral intellect and philosophical brain to help us determine who is the jerk on Reddit's "Am I The Asshole" 

Submit to Chuckle Mail:

All Our Socials: https://linktr.ee/chucklesandwich
